{"tid":606393,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪得小學有「主任」呢個概念？","createTime":"2018-03-26T12:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-27T16:01:19.000Z","uid":121961,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"bd7621417f55423ea629cf054ded3a464560b26c","tid":606393,"uid":121961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T12:25:48.000Z","msg":"記得小學寫簿面時<br />\n個miss好強調 係主任呀 唔好寫錯做老師<br />\n去到中學完全無聽過 陳主任 李主任etc<br />\n個個都係miss 呀sir"},{"pid":"fcce8b026992a86b2305eeb3981df1a2af95ba57","tid":606393,"uid":87573,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T12:27:43.000Z","msg":"搵小學生拎認同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13ef403e3d509b6044a76f0f449c2d1529268d0","tid":606393,"uid":135169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T12:28:20.000Z","msg":"主任仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bcc15dfbbb2b99a74002ab05772faf9c993f502","tid":606393,"uid":143582,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T12:28:30.000Z","msg":"中學都有主任，但唔會講出黎，佢地自己內部分"},{"pid":"8d88c6bd04e026a9b6d485fa4bdcd9fd77079509","tid":606393,"uid":170867,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T12:29:45.000Z","msg":"係牙 金日番去叫錯主任做miss-3-"},{"pid":"e642744b27e5e10efdbc3d62d82630270133319b","tid":606393,"uid":6132,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6bcc15dfbbb2b99a74002ab05772faf9c993f502","tid":606393,"uid":143582,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T12:28:30.000Z","msg":"中學都有主任，但唔會講出黎，佢地自己內部分"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T12:30:41.000Z","msg":"通常係科主任/訓導主任，不過有啲elective全校得自己一個教就冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858616f1d6c035d0a4eb56560fce4f7477be56e3","tid":606393,"uid":4618,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T12:34:53.000Z","msg":"上到u啲lecturer成日講自己最憎做subject leader，反而小學拎嚟兇班細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e62a59e65341182d939879e34b098f1af9e96899","tid":606393,"uid":116297,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T12:36:35.000Z","msg":"幼稚園都有主任 都係要叫x主任咁"},{"pid":"f1a4f9b380028a18e1d850a00e42a0aa9b329b0d","tid":606393,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:27:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上到u啲lecturer成日講自己最憎做subject leader，反而小學拎嚟兇班細路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似比人點去做多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8f8b3e8f32a383249205364e3ef9880669c2d5","tid":606393,"uid":67996,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:30:40.000Z","msg":"因為小學比較重階級觀念"},{"pid":"f59016b3f6d41a30309618872756f2b0503870cb","tid":606393,"uid":68219,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:48:42.000Z","msg":"小學有條姓黃既耶撚<br />\n做宗教主任果d咁既野<br />\n好撚鍾意捉鳩人唔叫佢黃主任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪因為咁 小學雞時期已經養成左對主任兩隻字既反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小五定小六果陣有個好好人既老師 係我地班class teacher黎<br />\n果年某次集會佢上台 職銜變左主任<br />\n返到課室已經全班一齊撚佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫左佢張主任叫左個幾禮拜<br />\n有次班主任堂佢好認真咁叫我地唔好叫佢主任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果陣佢做class teacher同一班跟左三年 對我地好nice<br />\n試過呻書包重 佢幫我托個袋托到返課室<br />\n仲試過上PE堂用個波唔小心踢到佢屎忽 佢笑下就無野<br />\n真心尊敬佢<br />\n張sir <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"937964d2d0f1e3462b78edaa09ab8bf8be479577","tid":606393,"uid":151143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:59:20.000Z","msg":"執返薪級表嚟睇，我估啲小學主任即係小學學位教師（PSM），其他啲普通老師就應該只係文憑教師（CM）或者助理小學學位教師（APSM）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但人工又唔夠中學嘅老屎忽高級學位教師（SGM）高，仍然諗唔到咁強調做主任嘅理由"},{"pid":"fa0c6f2ea6bfe79ca2166d7a2a017b28443bdf26","tid":606393,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T14:06:13.000Z","msg":"勁撚多主任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f0513ea78bfa3062c85d7e15ba6b15f00370a2","tid":606393,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T16:01:19.000Z","msg":"還有學科主任。"}]}